'''Office pour l'Information Eco-entomologique''' (abbreviated '''OPIE''' or '''OPIE-LR''', English: Office for Entomological Information) is a [[France|French]] government organisation based in [[Guyancourt]] devoted to [[entomology]], especially applied entomology.

